      VALUES ("I hope you enjoy my strategy and that it heklps all who wishes to learn his power. Magina is a hero that chooses when the fight starts and ends, he is a very powerful hero in this game we call DOTA. Enjoy", "The key thing here is survival and thats why you are buying the above items, because Magina is very weak at the start of the game what you need to do is last hit until you get enough money to complete the bracers. The tangos and ring of regen will help you to stay in the lane a little bit longer and also you would need the ring of regen to complete your Hood of Defiance.<br/>What you need to do is to get in a lane with a partner,an enemy intel hero, or a weak enemy hero. Try to avoid lanes where there are high hp heroes or heroes that are not mana dependent, the reason for this is that you wont be able to harass them as easily as a weak hero or an intel hero. I mentioned harass before, this is very simple to od with Magina, it involves blinking next to the hero in your lane when their creeps are almost destroyed attack them a few times and then blink back. You should do this when your blink is at either level 3 or 4, therefore you would get a few more attacks in than the hero and their mana would be low so they would have to use clarity potions or go back to base", "At this stage according to how fast the game is going your enmies may intend to push together in a lane or lanes according to how much players in the game. As the anti mage you can silently and patiently wait for a hero to accidently step to far forward to make it his last step. For example if you and your ally are pushing in a lane with two of your enemies it would be better to pick out one of the heroes( mainly the weaker one/intel hero) and kill him first while leaving the other one to be killed after by himself. ", "This is where you are most powerful because all of your opponents mana pool has increased by a large amount and at this point you should have your bashers and on your way to your butterfly. Therefore you with your fast attack speed together with your twin bashers and mana burn few heroes can stand in your way.", "Twin blades of death", "dotastrategy", "http://www.dotastrategy.com/strategy-4503-TwinBladesOfDeath.html", "Anti-Mage", "30");
