      VALUES ("The batman's role in the team is that(No he is not the savior of the weak) a ganker. He can be a semi-carry going to the late part of the game but he is more proficient as a ganker because of his skill firefly which can make heroes suffer from the large DPS it damage. That's why you need early boots.", "Sentinel Top/Scourge Bot - My comment to the lane you picked is that it is a dangerous lane because you get into the territory of the enemy and you are far from your tower. Yet, you are close to the two secret shops.<br/>Mid - Good lane for farming, rune whoring but bad for killing your enemy in the lane.<br/>Sentinel Bot/Scourge Top - One of my preferred lane, it's good because you are close to the tower which is a safe place. You can set-up ganks there because you are in your terf. A bad lane if you are lazy to defend towers.", "Ganking: First blink near the target, then cast lasso to the unit. After that, you go to your buddies while casting firefly dragging the enemy hero. Easy as that but you will have to do it fast because one wrong move can mean danger beause you are going to the territory of an enemy.<br/>Escaping: You know that you are fragile. So now that you have bink you can now easily escape any attacks. You can also use Firefly then go to unpassable terrains.<br/>Pushing: You will push after a gank or if you are aware of where the enemy heroes are. If you suceed with the gank or a clash, remember at least to push because you are confident that some of the heroes can not defend the tower. Spam your skills when a wave of creeps is coming. When youu are alone, just be aware of the map. If you see that heroes are busy then go push or use a clash from far in the place you are and push. Remmeber map-awareness.", "In this time of game, pushing and killing is a regular because at this point of the game those things are crucial. One kill can make a difference. So what is your role in this game? My answer support because you can farm hastily now since you are defending or pushing. So just be with your carry and support them. Go hunt some heroesin the jungle area and make them suffer. If the hero is escaping, just use SN and if you want to KS the carries then finish them with flame break. When you are defending just use the combo of what I've said earlier. If there are heroes just wait for your comrades and use the gank combo. Remember the road to success is having cooperation so in this time of the game just coordinate with your teammates. Don't disobey on them. Just have trust in them.", "Stop Drop Roll", "dotastrategy", "http://www.dotastrategy.com/strategy-32679-StopDropRollKeybisguidetoBatmaN.html", "Batrider", "30");
