      VALUES ("", "This is an defensive and harassing Broodmother in early game, and basically is a pushing machine because of your lane domination with your spiderlings. Your spiderlings can farm in the jungle for you while your are harassing your opponent(s) and in the same time have a decent amount of farm. You'll never have a mana problem because of the soul ring and health because of the 4HP regen of the web plus the 2 in the soul ring (more regen than a ring of health).", "In the mid stage of the game, you basicallly harass the spawn spiderlings in every low HP you see (creep or heroes) because you already have your orchid which is the main core item.<br/>The boots of choice will be most likely treads since you need that extra attack speed addition to your slow.<br/>Boots of Travel will be nice if you are a crazy freaking farmer, pusher and a pressure hitter on the enemy team. But only if you are farmed enough can you get this item. I recommend treads.", "you are almost unkillable with your ultimate popping up. Add a BKB and a satanic in your inventory then you have most likely 3 insane lives! Broodmother has the most life-saving ultimate if used correctly. You can change the course of a team fight if you work right. You can farm a lane, push a lane, dominate the game and kill anyone with this guide. Example: If you see a support hero walking out there alone, kill that guy and make him cry. Did I say that Butterfly is very useful in your ultimate? Right, I watched some tournaments last time and a player in Nirvana.cn used Broodmother and purchased a Butterfly at the 27th minute mark, he pops his ultimate but Lycanthrope is just bashing and killing the crap out of him, you know what? HE MISSED THE LAST HIT! Then Broodmother's ultimate is working and lifestealing like the 1/5 of his life. Living and killing Lycan, LYCAN WAS PISSED! Another items in addition, is the MKB and BKB, with MKB you can fight Mortred, pop your ultimate then kill him. BKB - you are pretty much unkillable because no one can right-click you to death while your ultimate is on and the Magic Immunity gives you that idea.", "Broodmother's Chaos", "dota2-builds", "http://www.dota2-builds.com/view-dota2-build.php?id=447", "Broodmother", "30");
