      VALUES ("Sticks and stones may break my bones, but words will make me go in a corner and cry by myself for hours.", "Don't use your level 1 orb to harrass the enemy as the damage is pitiful.  Instead use it to help you last hit.  You want to be super consevative since you can die easily with your pitiful health.  Focus on last hitting, but when your orb is level 3, you can use it to orb walk the enemy.  Remember that your orb affects towers as well.", "Go for your treads and orchids.  You should still be farming and not really helping your team out unless they need it.  You need to get items to be effective and yorur time is usually better spent farming.  You are good at ganking, though, because of your windwalk so if you see a low hp enemy that you think you can safely kill, go for it.  After you get your Orchids your ganking and general usefulness go through the roof and it is at this point that you can confidently join your team.  With strafe and searing arrows, you can take down towers fairly quickly.  Remember that one of the reason that bd protection was added in dota was because Clinkz was so good bding.", "Continue roaming with your windwalk for easy kills.  At the same time, you want to be farming for your skadi.  Skadi stacks with your orb so once you get that you're a lean, mean, undying DPS machine.  Don't be afriad to push on your own as long as you keep an eye out for potential ganks and when the enemy is coming.  Also, watch out for invis revealing items since those are your bane.  If a teamfight occurs, join it and dominate.", "Bony Thug", "", "", "Clinkz", "1");
