      VALUES ("this guide is all about in how natures attendants can save your life and your allies,, also natures attendants can make your creeps alive while fighting and pushing... with the skill nature attendants and untouchable making enchantress a hard to kill hero", "First buy 2 null talisman and go to the lower lane if sentinel side and higher lane if scourge side...in killing creeps just press ALT while moving your hero and just take the last shot on enemy creeps and also deny your creeps by pressing A on them, so that your enemy cannot level faster than you are.... also harass your enemy by taking him some shots and if running use your empetus.. DO NOT RIGHT CLICK YOUR EMPETUS!!.. also only go to your base if your enemy is going to there base too, when you are in your base buy boots of speed and ring of basillus and farm for MEKANSM..", "your items for now are  2 nulls, boots of speed, ring of basillus and mekansm.... you should have max out by then EMPETUS and Natures attendants... here in middle game you should watch out for your teammates,  if there are in trouble... dont forget to deny your creeps and always press ALT when killing a hero or there creeps... now you must farm for euls scepter.. euls is very helpful,it can help you from killing your enemy's and escaping them....and you can also use your euls to help your allies.... ", "well late game is where all hero's became really insane and tries to farm fast and will try and kill there enemy's fast.. well your items are 2 nulls,boots,ring of bassilus,mekansm and euls scepter....always use your skill well in fighting them... well try your best and hope that you will win the game like me", "Enchanted Enchantress", "dotastrategy", "http://www.dotastrategy.com/strategy-1657-EnchantedEnchantress.html", "Enchantress", "50");
