      VALUES ("Lich is a great support, good at controlling lanes, and is almost completely item independent. With his spammable nuke, auto deny that steals mana, chain ult and armor buff, all of this makes him a great addition to any team.", "In the early parts of the game stay in your lane and spam  Frost Blast to harass as often as you can, using to  Sacrifice to deny and get mana as much as possible, also if you are laning with a carry make sure to let them have all the farm.", "This is when ganking starts to happen, stay with your carry and make sure to keep denying and harassing, if your carry decides to gank go with him to help with the kill, but make sure not to last hit give the carry the xp, when team fights start to break out, keep up with the slows and your ult, just remember ult placement is key!!!! if you have  Ice Armor make sure to keep up with that and Meckansm too.", "Now that everyone is at a high level and your caries should be fed enough, make sure to keep on your mek and ice armor, if you do this combined with great ult placement your team should have no problem winning team fights.", "Acid's guide to Lich", "dotafire", "http://www.dotafire.com/dota-2/guide/acids-guide-to-lich-671", "Lich", "50");
