      VALUES ("Pros: +Awesome Ganker, +Anti-Tank, +Tank, +Carry, +Amazing Jungle Abilities<br/>Cons: -Ugly, -Mana Puddle, -Somewhat Item Dependent, -Really Ugly, -Rage Dispells Runes", " 1. Don't do anything stupid,  2. Retreat and heal if needed, 3. Creep pull if you feel like doing it that way. At level 6, regardless of whether or not you started in the jungle, you will go start to really abuse your potential. 1. Find a high level creep (level 5 or 6), 2. Infest it, 3. Devour it, 4. Violate more creeps. The ability to instant kill a high level creep provides you with a nice experience and gold advantage. Pretty soon you will be on your way to having some kickass items.", "Actual gank strategy: You grab an ally, You find a killable sucker, You attack that sucker like a noob.<br/>Situation 1, they try to take you on. Now is the time to start tanking it out. Activate RAGE and ARMLET then start whacking. For the next 5 seconds you are almost 100% immune to spells. It also gives you an attack speed boost, enjoy killing them. When FEAST stops being the most effective heal in the world (should they not be dead), use OPEN WOUNDS.With this, their fate is sealed and you have acquired another cherry.<br/>Situation 2, they leg it out of there. If your ally posesses a stun, let them use it, activate RAGE and ARMLET and get on top of them, when the stuns duration ends, it is time to OPEN some WOUNDS and continue your slaughter.<br/>Situation 3, they initiate their trap sequence. Things look bad, and for your ally, it probably will be, fortunately you have the best in antitrap technology. This time you activate RAGE and leg it for your enemies RANGED CREEP. INFEST and just stay there until your allies arrive to save your ass. (they will have to because if the enemy REALLY wants to kill you, they will need to push. If you have blink dagger now is a very good time to use it.", "In all honesty I would have liked you to win shortly after level 16, but lets just pretend that things haven't gone so well, you were arrested, Lina cried 'rape' and who knows what else happened. If this has happened, things have gone really badly. For the rest of the game, you will attack their thugly tank. The only logic is that, tanks make you tank. and thus you are harder to kill, from here you will start building up to fulfill your role as semi-tank-anti-tank-support hero.", "Grabbed by the Ghoulies (Jungle)", "dotastrategy", "http://www.dotastrategy.com/strategy-9082-GrabbedbytheGhouliesNaixaPainintheNuts.html#introduction", "Lifestealer", "55");
