      VALUES ("PROS:<br/>The skill that allows you to fight heavy tanks and survive to tell about it<br/>The skill that grants you magic immunity and attack speed<br/>The skill that slows the enemy and heals anyone who attacks the enemy<br/>The skill that hides you in creeps, allows you to kill them, regenerate HP and nuke in a 700 AOE<br/>Very decent Agility and Intelligence growth<br/>Superb casting animation<br/>Good starting Strength<br/>Rather easy last hits<br/>Above average movespeed <br/>Destroying enemy tanks is a huge ego and morale booster !<br/>Cons:<br/>In order to improve armor penetration, fights enemy tanks at effective range for its attacks, i.e. is melee<br/>Rather low Strength gain for a Strength hero<br/>No true escape mechanism<br/>No stun<br/>Low starting armor", "The first thing to do is whether you want to lane or jungle. If you're laning, stay back and just make some killing blows (last hits), and pray that you have a good fire support (babysitter). TDs are always kept in reserve and should be comitted to the frontline only when needed.<br/>Whatever way you choose, and because of the poor weather that maintains the area in the fog, ask your support units to set up observation posts (wards) for recon.", "Gather supplies (i.e. farm) as fast as possible in order to get your core. Then start ambushing (ganking) or make a frontal attack (push) to force the teamfights. Wars are won when fought efficiently ; don't target that infantry (low-HP support hero) that one of your mates can deal with. Combined arms is the key to victory ; distribute the spells and the firepower wisely on the enemy. Your targets' priority is as follow :<br/>1 or 2) Heavy tanks (You're the TD !)<br/>2 or 1) Carries<br/>3) Support heroes<br/>If there's an enemy heavy tank that also plays the role of carry, it's your priority target ! Make a short work of him !", "Never do anything alone ! Attack at 3 on 1, set up ambushes, use the appropriate units on the enemy ; use all the advantages that you could have !<br/>With some supplies, adapt your weaponry to what you're facing.", "Be a real tank destroyer", "playdota", "http://www.playdota.com/guides/be-a-real-tank-destroyer-", "Lifestealer", "50");
