      VALUES ("Slardar another hero who is rarely seen on the battlefield...for some unknown reason. Slardar has abilities that could easily kill heroes that are in their prime stages with a bink of an eye. Another hero killer...SLARDAR", "Game Start: Get a ring of Regen and Circlet. Pick either top or bottom.<br/>Farming: Get Last Hits. Deny.<br/>Pushing: Don't Push just yet.<br/>Killing: Well the good thing about Slardar is that he could also kill during the early game. Spam you slithereen crush when you get the chance. This gives you some advantage over your enemy. <br/>Fleeing: Use Sprint.", "Farming: Do not prioritize farming now. Farm only if you are underleveled or need cash.<br/>Pushing: Here you could start pushing. You are slowly becoming a tank so do not be afraid to get hit. Killing: This would be easy because now you have all you skills maxed. Killing during this part should follow this simple pattern:  SPRINT, CRUSH, AMPLIFY, WHACK, CHASE, KILL!!!. Seems simple enough. just remember not to underestimate the capabilities of your enemy alwasy be aware of your surroundings; are there still a lot of creeps with him, does he have items that could kill you, are you strong enough yet, does he have an ally with him? You must first look at these things before you attack. Do not be dependent on your amplify damage since it is not all the time that you would be able to kill him with it. So use it well use it wisely.", "Pushing: This is where you should start push into thenemy base. With Vlad's Offering your creeps could last longer. Also your damage will be higher.<br/> Killing: This is the pattern for Killing: Sprint, Crush, Amplify, Whack, Whack, Chase, KILL!!!<br/>Well here you should be really unstoppable since no one will be able to get to you. You are able to reach 522 ms with PT, Sprint and SnY so no noe will be able to run away or catch you. (Except for Balanar or Banehallow). Pushing here would be a must since you have to end the game alreayd so do it fats. Also do not prioritize on farming anymore expecially if you are lvl. 25 already so just farm if you want to help your allies with their items.", "Underated Slithereen", "dotastrategy", "http://www.dotastrategy.com/strategy-2417-TheUnderatedSlithereen.html#earlygame", "Slardar", "45");
