      VALUES ("Storm Spirit -  you need to learn when you will use his ultimate, how to use the combo kill in order and how to play him in the game. b4 game starts: before creeps starts to be summoned, after buying your starting items for 5 on 5 which is: animal courier, salve, tango, clarity, magic stick, go ahead to the mid lane, always mid lane,", "DONT GO FOR THE KILL UNTIL YOUR level 6, unless the support roamed in the middle lane(your lane), only FOCUS ON LAST HIT AND DENYING( the most important thing to do in early game and late game), if your enemy hero is a hero with no stun and is very soft its your lucky day, before level 6 you must have 2 null talismans and boots of speed but it would be better if you have build treads(int) before level 6, LEVEL6:  if your enemy hero is on top of the 1st towers hill, go to your own hill half near to your 1st tower then: BALL OF LIGHTNING( to your opponent, you must land at his back) -> HIT'EM! -> STATIC REMNANT(make sure it hits) -> HIT'EM, then he could die or have red hp, just use ball lighning to FINISH IT!, Destroy the tower, roam at your other lane that is getting pwned by the enemy and use the combo to a hero who is softer, and destroy the tower there", "WHEN CLASH: make sure 1 hero is missing from the other team(storm spirit should do that,which is you so kill 1 hero that is all alone from the enemy before clash) so your team has the advantage of wiping'em out, in this time you should have the build of: Power Treads, Orchid Malevolence, Linken Sphere, mystic staff, JUST KEEP LST HITTING WHEVER YOU HAVE FREE TIME<br/>HOW TO MOVE IN CLASH?: make sure your team mates go in first, after that, ball of lightning into the battlefield and destroy the enemy who has the lowest hp, back out when your recieving high damage or your linken is curently in cooldown, after the enemy team used all their stuns and magics land in again, and destroy'em all<br/>Mid Game COMBO: BALL OF LIGHTNING - HIT - VORTEX - HIT - REMNANT - HIT", "Late game(35-60 minutes): In this part you shoudve destroyed at least 5 towers, and your item should be: Treads(int), Orchid malevolence, linken, guinsoo, shiva, blood stone, if the game hasnt ended in the mid game, you should worry and start finishing the game cause you never know when the game will be opposite. <br/>Late Game COMBO: BALL OF LIGHTNING - HIT - VORTEX - HIT - REMNANT - GUINSOO - HIT HIT HIT HIT HIT HIT HIT - SHIVA(clash only)", "Storm Spirit's Typhoon body", "dota2-builds", "http://www.dota2-builds.com/view-dota2-build.php?hero=Storm-Spirit&id=485", "Storm Spirit", "50");
