      VALUES ("This guide emphasizes on Sven's role on the competitive scene. There are different builds for him but this is the most used. He is mainly an initiator but can also do quite decent dps for the team.", "Can do with top or bottom lanes: Choose a non-mid lane. He is a regular tri-lane guy because of his reliable AoE stun.<br/>Do what is expected from you: If you are in a tri-lane with a pure carry hero on your team then it is not your time to farm yet. Give the farm to your pure-carry. Always be aware of any kind of opportunity to kill your opponents. Do creep pulling if you are on your team's defensive lane. It's your chance to farm. <br/>Learn how to chain stuns: It is very crucial in teamfights to be able to maximize the stun duration on your targeted prey. If your teammate throws a stun at your opponent try to land some hits first. Right before the stun duration ends, throw your Storm Bolt skill. That way the target won't have time to be able to cast a skill to save himself. Do not give them the opportunity to escape.", "Farm for your items: This is your chance to get some items. Go straight for Dagger then Vanguard.<br/>Balance farming with ganking: If your teammates are going ganking, go with them. Farm the neutral camps along the way. Do not focus too much on farming. ", "Initiate for your team: Since you have an AoE stun and should have your Dagger right now, you should initiate for your team. Cast God's Strength, Blink beside your target, cast stun, warcy and whack away. <br/>Always try to stay alive: Once your life bar is critical try to escape, regen some hp and wait for stun and dagger cd. When it is both available blink in and stun a target once again if there are still more targets. Your carry might still need another disabling skill.<br/>If the game drags on, go for dps items: Try to bring down your target as swiftly as possible. You would also realize that when you do lethal damage to your target, your other opponents would also take tremendous amount of cleaved damage.", "Initiator Sven", "playdota", "http://www.playdota.com/guides/initiator-sven", "Sven", "60");
