      VALUES ("As you may know,Windrunner is from the few heroes who can fulfill 2 rules at the same time that called a Hybird hero.Like Visage which can be a Tank/Ganker or Invoker Who can almost play every role in games.", "If your team have a powerful solo laner hero (SF,Medusa,etc) give him/her the lane and go for a dual lane.Try to lane with a stuner/disabler hero.Never lane with a carry.You can choose whatever items you want.Like soloing,your early much be spent on harassing/denying and lasthiting.Try to net some kills with your mate because you know,Windrunner has good laning control.Just gank as much as possible but,try to get some farming done as well.", "By now you should have at last 2 or 3 of your cores.The only thing you should do is to gank as much as possible.Go for solo ganks only if you think you can handle your enemy by your own.Othewise,call your mates and gank with your mates.Use Focus Fire to get towers and always carry some TP scrolls.Try to push lanes if your not ganking and remember,put one eye on yhe minimap.Also buy and put wards if there's no1 buying wards.Always be coordinated with your team and like i said,never try KSing people.", "This is where you shine.By now you should have your luxury items.Just gank enemies and push lanes like hell in this phase of game.Here's amethod on how to killing enemies:<br/>1:Position yourself for a perfet shackle shot.<br/>2:Use shackle shot on your main enemy.<br/>3:Activate Focus Fire and use it on squishy carries or disablers.<br/>4:Activate windrunner if your gettin focused.<br/>5:Finish fleeing heroes with Power Shot or just cast Shackle Shot again.", "Fear my 1337 skills", "playdota", "http://www.playdota.com/guides/fear-my-1337-skills-", "Windrunner", "50");
